{"tid":1702430,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(舊聞) 闖列車快閃開逃生門 港鐵東涌線受阻50分鐘","createTime":"2019-11-09T16:38:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T02:39:46.000Z","uid":254330,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7486993907bde4ab097fa0de7b368b6fc0b94cbc","tid":1702430,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:38:07.000Z","msg":"講多次 係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">舊聞</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">好危險架,大家千祈唔好咁做</span><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】港鐵東涌線一列往東涌列車，昨午約5時抵南昌站時，突有最少4名戴口罩的男女闖入車尾駕駛室，將緊急逃生斜道放到路軌，致列車服務受阻約50分鐘。有資深車長稱，如行車時逃生裝置被啟動，乘客有跌出車廂的風險。<br />\n<br />\n死廢青,搞到我果日冇得番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地星期一11號朝頭早咪撚阻住我番工呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我要搭黨鐵番工架屌你"},{"pid":"1de84f721469ede09a08d9416277ed256f91941f","tid":1702430,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:39:44.000Z","msg":"純粹新聞分享, 大家千祈唔好咁做, 11號我要番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"068c4d1b90835c9e6abef99b73e8d1a5563b4aba","tid":1702430,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:42:48.000Z","msg":"我11號要番工架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d404a6e58ff7795a9c789cea1c6b596e7c369b3","tid":1702430,"uid":259611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:44:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08ee7f401e00f16d1a15524d3a81424864eba721","tid":1702430,"uid":254330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"c